author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Clear sealant application tips…I soak the Ultra Clear for 30 minutes in warm water. This makes it easier and smoother to apply between the backsplash/sink top and wall. I only tool it with my finger. This looks better than silicone and will remain clear 🔥 #bathroomremodel #sealant #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
